{"tid":670241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片睇】Samsung S9 新廣告狙擊 Apple iPhone","createTime":"2018-05-19T07:50:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T03:49:39.000Z","uid":64694,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"676639b4fa4811a5757a5a77d5b53c44b8e12529","tid":670241,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T07:50:18.000Z","msg":"三星（Samsung）和蘋果（Apple）的關係，大概就類似 Marvel 與 D.C. 一樣，經常針鋒相對。以往三星已經曾試過在廣告中向蘋果宣戰，取笑蘋果 iPhone 的各種機能都比不上三星的 Galaxy 系列。如今三星再度重施故技，拍攝廣告揶揄蘋果 iPhone 的性能。<br />\n<br />\n在三星全新拍攝的廣告 Moving On 中，描述一名 iPhone 6 用家，因為電池老化，導致電話反應遲緩，最需要 Apps 馬上反應的時候要等幾秒才有反應，更沒有防水功能。當她前去 Apple Store 尋找店員幫助時，店員只表示可以關閉電源管理功能，並建議該用家更換最新款的 iPhone。直到最後，她購買了 S9，所有問題就迎刃而解。<br />\n<br />\n在短短一分鐘的影片中，多次出現 S9 與 iPhone 6 的使用對比，甚至 iPhone 的戲分比 S9 更多。對此，外國科技網站《The Verge》撰文為蘋果抱不平，指三星將最新的電話與 iPhone 6 相比並不公，而 iPhone 6 的電池問題可以透過更換電池解決。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/05/18/samsung-vs-apple/mobile-phone/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F05%2F18%2Fsamsung-vs-apple%2Fmobile-phone%2Famp%2F&d=rcB%2BTCxZsq4If548uYZAxf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e5e8df8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/05/18/samsung-vs-apple/mobile-phone/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然我對iPhone感覺都麻麻，但都唔使咁樣踩人哋嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b257a1906dff80783bf26f4bcef5f11e023db84","tid":670241,"uid":64694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T07:52:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3qhW1sDPHYI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3qhW1sDPHYI&d=rcB%2BTCxZsq4If548uYZAxf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=5d6e41f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3qhW1sDPHYI</a>"},{"pid":"33c14a637cedcc7a37c3a297d2f637cd30caab6d","tid":670241,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T07:52:26.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆 用iphone6比都幾柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla